           class="flex flex-col items-center text-center bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm px-8 py-10 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-blue-100">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-9 h-9 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 7v5l3 3" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Economize tempo</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Automatize tarefas repetitivas e ganhe mais tempo para focar no que realmente importa: a educação.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-10 h-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500 mt-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200"
           class="flex flex-col items-center text-center bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm px-8 py-10 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-emerald-100">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-9 h-9 text-emerald-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 17l5-5 4 4 9-10" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 7h4v4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Centralize tudo</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Tenha todas as informações da sua escola em um único lugar, integradas e sempre atualizadas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-10 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 mt-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300"
           class="flex flex-col items-center text-center bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm px-8 py-10 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-purple-100">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-9 h-9 text-purple-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20H7a4 4 0 01-4-4V8a4 4 0 014-4h10a4 4 0 014 4v8a4 4 0 01-4 4z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 10h.01M12 10h.01M15 10h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Suporte eficiente</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Sempre conte com alguém a disposição para ajudar no uso do sistema.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-10 h-1 rounded-full bg-purple-500 mt-auto"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>


